<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000; /* Black */
            color: #fff; /* White */
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .professor-img {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 4px solid #8a3ab9; /* Purple */
        }
        .professor-img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .video-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 0;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .video-container video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #8a3ab9; /* Purple */
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ccc; /* Light Grey */
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #ddd; /* Lighter Grey */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <img src="IMG_4999.jpg" alt="Professor" class="professor-img">
            <div class="title">Mr. Jaydeep Kotadiya</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Founder of Mudberry Studio</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="title">Our Studio</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Open Hours: Monday to Saturday, 9 AM - 6 PM</p>
                <p>A brief description of your studio and its ambiance...</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="title">Our Story</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Established in 20XX</p>
                <p>Details about the history, vision, and mission of your pottery studio...</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
        <h2 class="title">Watch Our Studio</h2>
        <div class="video-container">
            <video width="640" height="360" controls>
                <source src="mudberryreel.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>